                                <iframe class="map-frame" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m28!1m12!1m3!1d1519.2319200388916!2d-3.707831032333791!3d40.4159516625807!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!4m13!3e0!4m5!1s0xd42289f6445f1b1%3A0x6b301c238b975d4a!2zSG90ZWwgQ2F0YWxvbmlhIEF0b2NoYSwgQy4gZGUgQXRvY2hhLCA4MSwgQ2VudHJvLCAyODAxMiBNYWRyaWQsIOCPveWMl-WAmeW-i-S4reaKue-8jO-8jO-8jO-8jA!3m2!1d40.4118358!2d-3.697807!4m5!1s0xd42288019e07577%3A0xf63989a319f36f6d!2zTWF5b3IgU3F1YXJlLCBQbGF6YSBNYXlvciwgTWFkcmlkLCDigJ3jgJPjgL_jgJXjgJvjgIXjgKHjgJbjgI_jgJzjgK7jgJPjgJvjgII!3m2!1d40.415511!2d-3.7074009!5e0!3m2!1szh-TW!2sjp!4v1722513904677!5m2!1szh-TW!2sjp"></iframe>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="font-semibold">西班牙小吃 (Tapas)：</span>
                            <p>可以在 **聖米格爾市場 (Mercado de San Miguel)** 體驗各種小點心。</p>
                        </li>
